{"article_id":"Pvm7M24bjfupHhYF","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Lois Lerner is toxic","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"-","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"and she knows it .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"|","depth":2},{"id":4,"text":"M.Scott Mahaskey/ Lerner speaks","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"Employers won ' t hire her .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"She ' s been berated with epithets like \" dirty Jew. \"","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Federal agents have guarded her house","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"because of death threats .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"And she ' s spent hundreds of thousands of dollars","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"defending herself against accusations","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"she orchestrated a coverup in a scandal","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"that has come to represent everything","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"Americans hate about the IRS .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"Lois Lerner is toxic -","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"and she knows it .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"But she refuses to recede into anonymity","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"or beg for forgiveness for her role in the IRS tea party-targeting scandal .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"\" I didn ' t do anything wrong , \"","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Lerner said in her first press interview","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"since the scandal broke 16 months ago .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"\" I ' m proud of my career and the job","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"I did for this country . \"","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Lerner ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"who sat down with in an exclusive two-hour session ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"has been painted in one dimension :","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"as a powerful bureaucrat","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"scheming with the Obama administration","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"to cripple right-leaning nonprofits .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Interviews with about 20 of her colleagues , friends and critics and a survey of emails and other IRS documents , however , reveal a much more complicated figure than the caricature","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"she ' s become in the public eye .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"The portrait","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"that emerges","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"shows Lerner is , indeed , fierce , unapologetic and perhaps even tone-deaf","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"when she says things","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"that show her Democratic leanings .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"She had a quick temper","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"and may have intimidated co-workers","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"who could have helped her out of this mess .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"It ' s easy to see how Republicans have seized on the image of a devilish figure","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"cracking down on conservative nonprofits .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"\" We followed the trail","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"where it leads ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"and we saw","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"it lead to Lois Lerner , \" House Oversight and Government Reform Chairman Darrell Issa","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"( R-Calif. )","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"said at a hearing Thursday .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"\" She refers with disdain to conservatives ;","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"she ' s an active liberal ;","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"and it ' s clear her actions were set out","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"to be detrimental to conservatives . \"","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"Yet Lerner is also described as \" apolitical \" and fair .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Some say","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"she was a generous boss","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"who inspired loyalty ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"baking brownies","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"and handing out lottery tickets to managers","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"to raise morale .","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"She ' s putting her babysitter ' s son through college","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"and in 2005 flew to New Orleans after Hurricane Katrina","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"to rescue animals .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"And she ' s a savvy lawyer :","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"She studiously avoided answering fundamental questions about her role in the IRS scandal","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"that could land her in deeper trouble with Congress .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"During her interview ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"flanked by her husband , a partner at a national law firm , and two of her personal attorneys ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"she opened up about her life as a pariah ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"joked about horrible news photos and advice","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"that she disguise herself with a blond wig ,","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"and cried","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"when expressing gratitude for her legal team ' s friendship .","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"Very few details of Lerner ' s personal history , professional background or life since her fall have been detailed in the news media .","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"One thing is clear :","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"She doesn ' t seem poised to back down","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"or give her Republican critics in Congress any satisfaction .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"\" Regardless of whatever else happens ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"I know","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"I did the best","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"I could under the circumstances","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"and am not sorry for anything","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"I did , \"","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"the 63-year-old said .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"On May 22 , 2013 , Lerner returned to the seeming safety of her IRS office","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"after invoking the Fifth Amendment","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"and being chased down a Capitol Hill hallway by the Washington press corps .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"Instead , she was summoned by the human resources department","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"and ordered to resign","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"or clean out her desk by 2 p.m.","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"and be escorted from the building on indefinite administrative leave .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"She refused to resign .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"It was a startling turnabout for the woman","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"whose alumni magazine said","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"she had \" rock star status \" in the tax world","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"and who was a recipient of a government service award for ethics .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"She thought","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"she was months away from a quiet retirement","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"after 33 years working for Uncle Sam .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"\" Under both Republican and Democratic administrations , she got these amazing ratings and bonuses . ...","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"And","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"once she retired ,","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"she would have gone out with bells and whistles ,","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"and the IRS commissioner would have made a speech . ...","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"It went from that to :","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"You ' re under criminal investigation ,","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"and your career is ruined , in a week , \"","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"said Lerner ' s husband , Michael Miles ,","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"who sat to her right during the interview .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"The beginning of the end started a few days earlier ,","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"when acting IRS Commissioner Steven Miller asked her to get ahead of a damning inspector general report due the following week .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"It detailed IRS agents","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"giving heightened scrutiny to nonprofits","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"using words like \" tea party , \" \" patriot \" and \" limited government spending , \"","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"and asking the groups inappropriate questions about their donors and political affiliations .","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"Lerner ,","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"then head of the division","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"handling organizations","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"claiming tax-exempt status ,","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"obliged","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"and dropped what turned out to be a political bombshell at an American Bar Association conference ,","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"using a planted question","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"to apologize for the treatment of right-leaning nonprofits from IRS \" front-line people \" in Cincinnati .","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"Within days , lawmakers in both parties were calling for her resignation ,","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"furious","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"that IRS leaders ,","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"including Lerner ,","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"had withheld information","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"when asked by lawmakers for months about the matter .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"Top officials also blamed Cincinnati ,","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"when , in fact , Washington was also handling the cases .","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"Called to testify before the House Oversight Committee ,","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"Lerner decided to take the Fifth","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"and read a defiant speech","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"declaring her innocence","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"- one","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":135,"text":"Republicans argued","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"waived her rights .","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"She says","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"she ' d do it again .","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"\" By taking the Fifth ,","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"Lois put a sign on her back :","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"Kick me , \"","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"said Paul Streckfus , editor of the EO Tax Journal .","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"\" To the average person , that sounds like , ' Oh my God , she must be hiding something ! ' \"","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"Lerner , for her part , assumes","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"she is at the center of the storm","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"because \" I was the person","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"who announced it .","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"I assume","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"the other part of it is because I declined to talk ,","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"and","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"once I declined to talk ,","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"they could say anything","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"they wanted ,","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"and they knew","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"I couldn ' t say anything back . \"","depth":13}],"relations":[{"parent":311,"left":159,"right":310,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":159,"left":158,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":0,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":310,"left":177,"right":309,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":177,"left":4,"right":176,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":176,"left":167,"right":175,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":167,"left":5,"right":166,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":166,"left":6,"right":165,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":165,"left":160,"right":164,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":160,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":9,"right":163,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":161,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":168,"right":174,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":14,"ri